# HUD::SET_BLIP_NAME_FROM_TEXT_FILE

## Summary
Change Radar blip name with text from text file

## Parameters
* **BLIP_INDEX** blip
* **STRING** textLabel

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Doesn't work if the label text of gxtEntry is >= 80.
